<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd">

<en-note><div><div><font style="font-size: 24pt;"><span style="font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;">Vue03</span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 24pt;"><span style="font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(186, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">一 .&nbsp; 动画</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 单元素/组件的过渡:</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Vue提供了transition的封装组件</div><div>例:&nbsp;</div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;div id=&quot;app&quot;&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;toggle&quot; @click=&quot;flag=!flag&quot;&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;transition&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;h3 v-if=&quot;flag&quot;&gt;这是一个h3标签&lt;/h3&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/transition&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">var vm = new Vue({</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;el: &apos;#app&apos;,</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;data: {</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flag: false</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;methods: {}</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;})</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; .v-enter,</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.v-leave-to {</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;opacity: 0;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;transform: translateX(150px);</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</font></span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.v-enter-active,</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.v-leave-active{</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;transition: all 0.8s ease;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</font></span></div></div><div>过渡的类名:</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 在进入/离开的过渡中,共有6个class类:</div><ol style="margin: 1.2em 0px -1.2em; padding-bottom: 1.2em; z-index: 1; padding-left: 1.5em; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-enter</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">：定义进入过渡的开始状态。在元素被插入时生效，在下一个帧移除。</span></li><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-enter-active</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">：定义过渡的状态。在元素整个过渡过程中作用，在元素被插入时生效，在</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">transition/animation</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">完成之后移除。这个类可以被用来定义过渡的过程时间，延迟和曲线函数。</span></li><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-enter-to</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">:</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.6em;">2.1.8版及以上</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">定义进入过渡的结束状态。在元素被插入一帧后生效 (于此同时</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-enter</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">被删除)，在</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">transition/animation</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">完成之后移除。</span></li><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-leave</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">: 定义离开过渡的开始状态。在离开过渡被触发时生效，在下一个帧移除。</span></li><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-leave-active</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">：定义过渡的状态。在元素整个过渡过程中作用，在离开过渡被触发后立即生效，在</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">transition/animation</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">完成之后移除。这个类可以被用来定义过渡的过程时间，延迟和曲线函数。</span></li><li><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-leave-to</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">:</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.6em;">2.1.8版及以上</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">定义离开过渡的结束状态。在离开过渡被触发一帧后生效 (于此同时</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">v-leave</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">被删除)，在</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">transition/animation</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="word-spacing: 0.05em; position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; line-height: 1.6em;">完成之后移除。</span></li></ol><div><en-media hash="d39d7df168eb5a35fabf315528b9d6d5" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 24pt;" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold;">修改v-前缀:</span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">对于这些在</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">enter/leave</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">过渡中切换的类名，</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">v-</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">是这些类名的前缀。使用</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&lt;transition name=&quot;my-transition&quot;&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">可以重置前缀，比如</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">v-enter</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">替换为</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); border-radius: 2px; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(233, 105, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, Monaco, courier, monospace; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">my-transition-enter</span><span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0.75px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal;">。</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="word-spacing: 0.75px;"><font style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(186, 0, 255); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">使用animate.css动画:&nbsp;</span></font></span></div><div><br/></div><div><a href="https://daneden.github.io/animate.css/" style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 165); color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;;-evernote-highlight:true;">https://daneden.github.io/animate.css/</a></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 注意:&nbsp; 在添加类中要添加animated类</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; :duration:&nbsp; 绑定动画时间,可通过对象来设置进入离开时的时间</div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;transition</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;enter-active-class=&quot;bounceIn&quot;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;leave-active-class=&quot;bounceOut&quot;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;:duration=&quot;{ enter: 200,leave: 400 }&quot;&gt;</font></span></div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <b><font color="#5DDAFF">//注意: 不能使用行内元素</font></b></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;h3 v-if=&quot;flag&quot; class=&quot;animated&quot;&gt;这是一个h3标签&lt;/h3&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/transition&gt;</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(186, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">使用钩子函数模拟小球半场变化:</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div>使用transition把小球包裹起来,在属性添加javascript钩子函数</div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</span> <span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &lt;transition</font></span></font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@before-enter=&quot;beforeEnter&quot;</font></span></font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@enter=&quot;enter&quot;</font></span></font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@after-enter=&quot;afterEnter&quot;&gt;</font></span></font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;div class=&quot;ball&quot; v-show=&quot;flag&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</font></span></font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(186, 0, 255);"><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/transition&gt;</font></span></font></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> <span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;methods: {</font></span></div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <font color="#F14F9A">//注意: 动画钩子函数的第一个参数: el,表示要执行动画的那个DOM元素,是个原生的JS DOM对象</font></div><div><font color="#F14F9A">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //大家可以认为,&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Monaco;"><font style="font-size: 9pt;">el 是通过 document.getElementById(&apos;&apos;) 方式获取到的原生JS DOM对象</font></span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;beforeEnter(el){</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font color="#F14F9A">&nbsp;// beforeEnter 表示动画入场之前，此时，动画尚未开始，可以 在 beforeEnter 中，设置元素开始动画之前的起始样式</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;"><font color="#F14F9A">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;// 设置小球开始动画之前的，起始位置</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;el.style.transform = &apos;translate(0,0)&apos;;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;enter(el,done){</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco;"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;"><font color="#F14F9A">// 这句话，没有实际的作用，但是，如果不写，出不来动画效果；</font></span></font></span></div><div><font color="#F14F9A"><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 可以认为 el.offsetWidth 会强制动画刷新</span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;el.offsetWidth;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco;"><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;"><font color="#F14F9A">// enter 表示动画 开始之后的样式，这里，可以设置小球完成动画之后的，结束状态</font></span></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;el.style.transform = &apos;translate(150px,500px)&apos;;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;el.style.transition = &apos;all 1s ease&apos;;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco;"><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <font color="#F14F9A">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;">// 这里的 done， 起始就是 afterEnter 这个函数，也就是说：done 是 afterEnter 函数的引用</span></font></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;done();</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;afterEnter(el){</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco;"><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt;"><font color="#F14F9A">// 动画完成之后，会调用 afterEnter</font></span></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;this.flag = !this.flag;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div></div><div><font style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(229, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">列表动画</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div>注意:&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.&nbsp;在实现列表过渡的时候,如果需要过渡的元素,是通过v-for循环渲染出来的,不能使用transition 包裹,需要使用transitionGroup</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. 如果要为v-for循环创建的元素添加动画,需要为每个人元素添加:key属性</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 3. 给transition-group标签添加appear属性,实现刚展示出来,入场时候的动画效果</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4. 通过为transition-group标签添加tag属性,指定transition-group渲染为指定元素,如果不指定tag属性,则默认渲染为span 标签</div><div>如果要是删除时的过渡:</div><div><en-media hash="48a3abe443ae8862d75ab2598da77686" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 24pt;"><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: rgb(186, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">二.&nbsp; &nbsp;组件</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 173, 224);"><b>什么是组件?</b></font></div><div>组件的出现,就是为了拆分Vue实例的代码量的,能够让我们以不同的组件来划分不同的功能模块,将来我们需要什么功能,就可以去调用对应的组件即可</div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(26, 173, 224);"><b>模块化和组件的不同?</b></font></div><div><span>&nbsp; &nbsp;模块化:&nbsp; &nbsp;是从代码逻辑的角度进行划分的; 方便代码分层开发, 保证每个功能模块的职能单一</span><br/></div><div><span><span>&nbsp; &nbsp;组件化:&nbsp; &nbsp;是从UI界面的角度进行划分的; 前端的组件化,方便UI组件的重用</span><br/></span></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>创建全局组件的几种方式:</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(241, 79, 154);">1.&nbsp; 使用vue.extend创建全局组件</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;使用vue.component(&apos;组件名称&apos;,创建出来的组件模板对象)</div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;var com1 = Vue.extend({</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;template: &apos;&lt;h3&gt;这是使用 Vue.extend 创建的组件&lt;/h3&gt;&apos; // 通过 template 属性，指定了组件要展示的HTML结构</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;})</font></span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://vue.component/" style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Vue.component</a><span style="font-family: Monaco; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">(&apos;myCom1&apos;, com1)</span></font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(241, 79, 154);">2.&nbsp; 创建全局组件的第二种方式</span></div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<en-media hash="31620e3f5c23456b33313811af03b508" type="image/png"/></div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 注意:&nbsp; 不论是哪种方式创建出来的组件.组件的template属性指向的模板内容,必须有且只能有一个根元素</div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span> <span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(241, 79, 154);">&nbsp; 3.&nbsp; 创建全局组件的第三种方式</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;在被控制的#app外面,使用template元素,定义组件的HTML模板结构</span></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&lt;template id=&quot;tmpl&quot;&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;div&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;h1&gt;这是通过 template 元素,在外部定义的组件结构,这个方式,有代码的只能提示和高亮&lt;/h1&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;h4&gt;好用,不错!&lt;/h4&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/template&gt;</font></span></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><a href="http://vue.component/" style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Vue.component</a><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">(&apos;mycom3&apos;, {</span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;template: &apos;#tmpl&apos;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;})</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(229, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">组件中的data和methods</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div><ol start="1"><li>组件可以有自己的data数据</li><li>组件中的data和实例的data有点不一样,实例中的data可以为一个对象,但是组件中的data必须是一个方法</li><li>组件中的data除了必须为一个方法之外,这个方法内部,还必须返回一个对象才行</li><li>组件中的data数据,使用方式,和实例中的data使用方式完全不同</li></ol></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(229, 0, 255); font-weight: bold;">组件的切换方式:</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div><en-media hash="cc23b589b86f60ca985c1a5b8f0309b7" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div><en-media hash="0f8e977ef4db0da828b0e281ff8cf8f0" type="image/png"/></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">组件切换--切换动画:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 通过transition标签将component标签包裹起来,通过 mode 属性,设置组件切换时候的模式</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">例:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<en-media hash="d4f7fd2bc9e8054d474fcdff89ccfe97" type="image/png"/></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>]]></content><created>20171227T011444Z</created><updated>20180105T120829Z</updated><note-attributes><author>1501627915@qq.com</author><source>desktop.win</source><source-url>https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/transitions.html#%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E6%B8%A1</source-url><source-application>evernote.win32</source-application></note-attributes><resource><data encoding="base64">
