<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd">

<en-note><div><font style="font-size: 24pt;"><span style="font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;">Gulp</span></font></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">[官网] (</span><a href="http://www.gulpjs.com/" style="font-family: Monaco;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 250, 165);-evernote-highlight:true;">http://www.gulpjs.com</a><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">)</span></b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 11pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">[中文网] (</span><a href="http://www.gulpjs.com.cn/" style="font-family: Monaco;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 250, 165);-evernote-highlight:true;">http://www.gulpjs.com.cn</a><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">)</span></b></font></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font color="#3665EE" style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>gulp 的五个核心方法:</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">1. 创建任务:</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">gulp.task(&apos;任务名&apos;,function(){})</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">2. 指定想要处理的文件:</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">gulp.src(&apos;./*.css&apos;)</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">3. 指定最终处理后的文件存放路径:</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">gulp.dest()</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">4. 自动监视文件的变化, 然后执行相应任务:</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">gulp.watch()</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">5. 直接执行相应的任务:</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">gulp.run(&apos;任务名&apos;)</font></b></font></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>安装gulp:</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`</font><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">npm i gulp-cli -g`</font></b></font></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><b>gulp 的使用:</b></div><div><b>1. 在当前项目中也要安装 gulp:&nbsp;<font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`npm i gulp --save`</font></b></div><div><b>2. 还需要在当前项目中新建一个文件: <font color="#7600D8" style="font-size: 14pt;">gulpfile.js(在此文件中写打包代码)</font></b></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 9pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">var gulp =&nbsp;&nbsp;require(&apos;gulp&apos;);</font></span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;// 创建任务</span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;// 第一个参数: 任务名</span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;// 第二个参数: 回调函数,当我们执行任务时就会执行这个函数</span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 9pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 9pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;gulp.task(&apos;test&apos;, function(){</font></span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco;"><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;console.log(123)</font></span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco;"><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;})</font></span></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco; font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">3.&nbsp; 执行任务:&nbsp;</span> <span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: Monaco;"><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`gulp 任务名`</font></span></div></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font color="#3665EE" style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>对js 进行打包:</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>1) 对js进行压缩的包</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`npm i gulp-uglify --save`</font></b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>2) 对js进行合并操作的包</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span> <font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;`npm i gulp-concat --save`</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><font color="#000000" style="font-size: 10pt;">3) 导入模块包</font></b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="cc484aec9907d92c0dc4c9e4d920d103" type="image/png"/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>4) 写入打包代码</b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="c8aa4c3e398b6a6562f847275c1fb162" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font color="#3665EE" style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>对css进行打包操作:</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>1) css压缩的包</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`npm i gulp-cssnano --save`</font></b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;或</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`npm i gulp-cssmin --save`</font></b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>2) 合并的包与打包js相同</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>3) 引入包:(如果是gulp-cssnano,则引入gulp-cssnano)</b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="537762c67f8a0ef4776fb2b20eec1044" type="image/png"/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>4) 打包代码</b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="064238229ed082e96b281ae0830a9b26" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font color="#3665EE" style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>对html进行压缩:</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>1) 对html进行压缩的包:</b></font></div><div><font><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><font color="#FF0000" style="font-size: 11pt;">`npm i gulp-htmlmin --save`</font></b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/kangax/html-minifier" style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">https://github.com/kangax/html-minifier</a></b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>2) 合并的包与js相同</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>3) 引入包</b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="f7fdbb90f5cb541eb2aeb1cb98c0f843" type="image/png"/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>4) 打包代码</b></font></div></div><div><en-media hash="ea5216d06d326812df62ec0da7e5a166" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div><font style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(222, 87, 0);">了解内容:</font></div><div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>gulp.watch</b></font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">-</span><span style="font-family: Monaco;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Monaco;">监视文件的变化，然后执行相应的任务</span></b></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>gulp.run</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>- 直接执行指定的任务</b></font></span></div></div><br/></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);-en-codeblock:true;"><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;// gulp.watch 监视文件变化，执行相应任务</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;gulp.task(&apos;mywatch&apos;, function(){</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;<span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>// 执行指定的任务</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>gulp.run(&apos;script&apos;)</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;// 1.监视js文件的变化，然后执行script任务</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>// 第一个参数：要监视的文件的规则</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>// 第二个参数：是要执行的任务</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;gulp.watch([&apos;./app.js&apos;,&apos;sign.js&apos;],[&apos;script&apos;])</b></font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Monaco; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>&nbsp;})</b></font></span></div></div><div><en-media hash="688c69151098db1a65a578c852b8dfde" type="image/png"/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>]]></content><created>20180105T124649Z</created><updated>20180105T132800Z</updated><note-attributes><author>1501627915@qq.com</author><source>desktop.win</source><source-application>evernote.win32</source-application></note-attributes><resource><data encoding="base64">
